name: Modern
description: Sleek and functional design with clean lines, high-gloss finishes, and built-in appliances.

name: Traditional
description: Classic design with ornate cabinets, rich colors, and a focus on comfort and warmth.

name: Rustic
description: Earthy tones, wooden accents, and vintage appliances create a warm, cozy feel.

name: Industrial
description: Exposed brick, metal accents, and stainless steel appliances give it an edgy, urban look.

name: Minimalist
description: Simple, clutter-free space with neutral colors, flat-front cabinets, and hidden appliances.

name: Scandinavian
description: Bright and airy design with natural wood, white surfaces, and a focus on functionality.

name: Farmhouse
description: A cozy, traditional kitchen with wooden cabinetry, a farmhouse sink, and rustic decor.

name: Bohemian
description: Eclectic and colorful design with open shelving, artistic tiles, and unique decor.

name: Mid-Century Modern
description: Retro-inspired with wood cabinetry, bright colors, and sleek, minimal appliances.

name: Luxury
description: High-end materials, marble countertops, and top-of-the-line appliances create a premium kitchen.

name: Eclectic
description: A mix of styles with vibrant colors, bold patterns, and unique, personalized details.

name: Transitional
description: A blend of traditional and contemporary elements for a balanced, timeless design.
